Salesforce Analytics Tools

Reports and Dashboards

Manage Your Reports and Dashboards on Analytics Home

Reports
Dashboards

Organize Dashboards

Keep your dashboards at your fingertips by embedding them around Salesforce, printing them, or deleting dashboards that you don’t need anymore.

Embed Dashboards on the Home Tab and in Lightning Apps
Change Dashboard Owner
Transfer dashboard ownership if responsibilities change or the current dashboard owner leaves your organization.

Print a Dashboard
Print dashboards using your browser’s print option.
Download a Dashboard to a PNG File
Download your dashboard as a PNG file that you can embed in presentations or refer to wherever you are.
Delete a Dashboard
It’s a good idea to delete dashboards that you no longer need.

Install the CRM Sample Dashboards from AppExchange
Use these dashboards from the AppExchange as a starting point for building dashboards that meet your business needs.
Install the Preconfigured Sales Cloud Dashboards from AppExchange

Work with Dashboards 

Post Lightning Dashboards to Slack
title: Organizing Salesforce Dashboards
